KANSAS ADMINISTRATIVE REGULATIONS
4-8-13.
Service of notices and statements.
Notices and statements required by K.S.A. 2-1320 shall be deemed sufficient when given by serving: Upon the landowner or his agent or trustee; upon the executor or administrator of an estate of a deceased landowner; upon the guardian of the estate of a minor or other person under legal disability; or upon one of several joint owners; or, one of several tenants in common; by either: (a) Personal delivery; (b) certified mail.
Such notices and statements may be served by either: (a) The county, district, or city weed supervisor; (b) a county commissioner; (c) the sheriff; (d) a member of the governing body of a city, or the marshal, or a policeman of any city, having jurisdiction over land described in notice or statement.
4-8-14a.
Definitions.
(a) "2,4-D" means (2,4-dichlorophenoxy) acetic acid.
(b) "Bromacil" means 5-bromo-6-methyl-3-(1-methylpropyl)-2,4(1H,3H) pyrimidinedione.
(c) "Chlorsulfuron" means 2-chloro-N-[[(4-methoxy-6-methyl-1,3,5- triazin-2-y1)amino] carbonyl]
(d) "Clopyralid" means (3,6-dichloro-2-pyridinecarboxylic acid).
(e) "Dicamba" means 3,6-dichloro-2-methoxybenzoic acid.
(f) "Fenoxaprop-ethyl" means (Ã¯Â¿Â½)-ethyl 2-[-4-[(6-chloro-2-benzoxazolyl) oxy]phenoxy]
(g) "Fluazifop-P" means (R)- 2-[4[[5-(trifluoromethyl)-2-pyridinyl]oxy]
(h) "Fosamine" means ethyl hydrogen (aminocarbonyl) phosphonate.
(i) "Glyphosate" means N-(phosphonomethyl) glycine.
(j) "Imazapic" means (Ã¯Â¿Â½)-2-[4,5-dihydro-4-methyl-4-(1-methylethyl)-5-oxo-1H-imidazol-2-yl]- 5-methyl-3 pyridinecarboxylic acid.
(k) "Imazapyr" means (Ã¯Â¿Â½)-2-[4,5-dihydro-4-methyl-4-(1-methylethyl)-5-oxo-1H- imidazol-2-yl] -3-pyridinecarboxylic acid.
(l) "MSMA" means monosodium methanearsonate.
(m) "Metsulfuron Methyl" means methyl 2-[[[[(4-methoxy-6-methyl-1,3, 5-triazin-2-yl) amino]carbonyl]
(n) "Nicosulfuron" means 2-[[[[(4,6-dimethoxy-2-pyrimidinyl)amino]carbonyl]
(o) "Picloram" means 4-amino-3, 5, 6-trichloro-2-pyridinecarboxylic acid.
(p) "Primisulfuron" means methyl 2-[[[[[4,6-bis(difluoromethoxy)-2-pyrimidinyl] amino]
(q) "Sethoxydim" means 2-[1-(ethoxyimino)butyl]-5-[2-(ethylthio)propyl]
(r) "Sulfometuron" means methyl 2-[[[[(4,6-dimethyl-2-pyrimidinyl)amino] carbonyl]
(s) "Tebuthiuron" means N-[5-(1,1-dimethylethyl)-1,3,4-thiadiazol-2-y1]-N,N'- dimethylurea.
(t) "Triclopyr" means [(3,5,6-trichloro-2-pyridinyl)oxy]acetic acid.
(u) "Trifluralin" means 2,6-dinitro-N,N-dipropyl-4- (trifluoromethyl)benzenamine.
